highlights.text: Diego Mitre has the most spots on Viral Songs South Korea. “Flaming Thunder God (from "Demon Slayer: Infinity Castle") - Cover” is the highest at #3.
“PAYE” by MUSHVENOM is the highest new entry on Viral Songs South Korea at #82.
“おつかれSUMMER” by HALCALI has been on Viral Songs South Korea the longest, at 128 days straight.
“Confess Your Love” by Jiandro and ola.wav is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs South Korea, up 20 spots at #20.
